<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> The robe is awarded to people who can use it the most in a raid situation. Peridots arnt gonna go to the chanter to rune herself so she can stay at FM instead of 70m the whole time, there gonna go to the GB/DB wizard who uses them far more effectively. And with the wiz epic, we dont have to spend 20pp to get a blue bub of mana, because ours is free. You see where im coming from <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
