I don't know many enchanter for whom mana is a problem. Perhaps if you are the only one with Kois, but the amount that spell drops, I'd be surprised. <br>
<br>
As to casting intellectual superiority for THO, thats pretty pointless, just get the aoe removed, as you still fizzle loads with superiority once aoe'd.<br>
<br>
I barely think its a worthwhile item on a wizard with infinite free runes, let alone a chanter.<br>
<br>
As to getting 20% mana from one epics worth of dmg, you must have an int of 100 or something. Assuming you have 3500 mana, 800 hp at a 3:1 ratio is 260 mana. Thats closer to 13% and you lose out on your med ticks doing it. <p><CENTER>
