manarobe gives 40 mana per tick as long as this number is greater than normal medding, you're going to benefit from the manarobe.... <br>
the thing is on my server, they are /very/ rare... i'd say 7-8<br>
on the server... i've seen them on mostly wizards, with an enchanter and a mage also having one if i recall correctly, i think both enchanter and wizard can put this to use to increase their mana regen... especially in conjunction with a shaman to cast torpor on them, i loan my manarobe to my chanter friend quite frequently on larger raids, if you think it doesn't help their class, you're nuts, it helps pretty much every class minus necros with their hp&gt;mana series of spells...<br>
